1
00:00:32,241 --> 00:00:38,038
ALAM SEMESTA KITA

2
00:00:44,711 --> 00:00:46,672
Biarkan saya selesai bicara.

3
00:00:48,840 --> 00:00:52,427
Berdasarkan tinjauan komprehensif atas semua dokumen dan cerita Anda.

4
00:00:52,511 --> 00:00:53,804
kalian berdua

5
00:00:54,429 --> 00:00:56,098
